"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## Are NFTs sustainable investments or just a short-term hype?\\n\\nA friend of mine recently asked me: How can I make money in NFTs? Are NFTs a sustainable investment or just a short-term hype? Both are fair questions and having followed Web3 closely this year, I appreciate this opportunity to make sense of NFTs in 2022 from the perspective of a retail investor. Bear with me as I'm learning in public here, and please let me know your feedback on Twitter ([@Copenstrand](https://twitter.com/copenstrand)). None of this is financial advice but solely my opinion.\\n\\n### A quick recap of 'NFT summer'\\n\\nLet's rewind to March 2021: The moment [Beeple's collage sold as an NFT for $69 million](https://www.theverge.com/2021/3/11/22325054/beeple-christies-nft-sale-cost-everydays-69-million), the word ‘non-fungible token (NFT)’ entered into our shared vocabulary to describe scarce, differentiable, programmable digital assets.\\n\\nWhile you don't care which bitcoin you own and treat them all as interchangeable, in crypto, we call ‘numbered’ tokens NFTs as they are clearly differentiable. Similar to how we value uniqueness in real life, NFTs allow us to value uniqueness in digital assets. As a speculative asset, the more demand for an NFT exists and the rarer its properties and supply, the higher the price. You might appreciate [Punk 6529’s thread if you struggle with the concept](https://twitter.com/punk6529/status/1451896453065023493) and [this thread by Mags.eth if you struggle with terms](https://twitter.com/magdalenakala/status/1430651402611675139).\",\"timestamp\":1642408922,\"title\":\"Thoughts on investing in NFTs in 2022\"},\"digest\":\"T2wS38e-5VocB3IzBpWKcHmWWTE_a3rQBuIa9CXGJTI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x55F7E68ad9FA326034cc630b7CE014E8D836B255\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cMIIKXUffp1bUvpL5biVyQFa_hOMrC0poafHmGqLVn0\\\",\\\"